{"lemma":"حَشِيشُ","slug":"حَشِيشُ","root":"ح.ش.ش","root_slug":"ح-ش-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ش-ش","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8062"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B4%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B4%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"grass, hay","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hemp, cannabis; marijuana","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hemp, cannabis; hashish","tags":["collective"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.ʃiːʃ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8062","headword_ar":"حَشِيشٌ","root":"H$","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dry herbage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dry pasture,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fodder:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Fárábee, S, Mgh, Msb, K:) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEilN","text_ar":"فَاعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) what is fresh is not so called: (S, Msb:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eu$obN","text_ar":"عُشْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to what is fresh and what is dry: this, says ISd, is the opinion of the generality of the lexicologists: some [he adds] assert that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"H$y$","text_ar":"حشيش"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"green pasture"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but he says that this is not correct; [and the like is said in the Msb;] for this word is properly applied to denote dryness and contraction: ISh says that it is applied to all"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leguminous plants, fresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dry;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalafN","text_ar":"عَلَفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalFY","text_ar":"خَلًى"},{"kind":"text","text":": Az says that when they use it unrestricted, the Arabs mean thereby"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaliY~","text_ar":"حَلِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herb called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naSiY~","text_ar":"نَصِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when it has become dry and white,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] in particular; and that this is the best kind of fodder; that horses thrive upon it, and it is one of the best pastures for camels, or for camels and sheep and goats; a good supply in years of scarcity: (TA:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cut herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasture;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) the n. un. is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a fascicle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wisp, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$y$","text_ar":"حَشيش"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a herb of any kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$aAy^i$u","text_ar":"حَشَايِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [It is also applied, in the present day, to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Hemp,"},{"kind":"text","text":"used for its intoxicating property; both"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dry:"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy$u","text_ar":"حَشِيشُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaraAfiy$i","text_ar":"الحَرَافِيشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banojN","text_ar":"بَنْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.: and also termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy$apN AlfaqaraA='i","text_ar":"حَشِيشَةٌ الفَقَرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see De Sacy's “ Chrest. Arabe, ”, see. ed., vol. i. pp. 210-283. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy$apu","text_ar":"حَشِيشَةُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~uloTaAni","text_ar":"السُّلْطَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xarodalN","text_ar":"خَرْدَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$iy$N","text_ar":"حَشِيشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one, that has dried up in the belly of its mother;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$~N","text_ar":"حَشٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maHo$uw$N","text_ar":"مَحْشُوشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uHo$uw$N","text_ar":"اُحْشُوشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hu$~N","text_ar":"حُشٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and the rest],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one, that perishes in the belly of its mother."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA^aloqato H$iy$FA","text_ar":"فَاَلْقَتْ حشِيشًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And she cast forth a child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young one, dried up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqato waladahaA Ha$iy$FA","text_ar":"اَلْقَتْ وَلَدَهَا حَشِيشًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cast forth her young one dried up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","S","TA"]}]}}